<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thihna luiguom kana chieh pai ding ka hi,
 Mahleh Hukdampa vennan chieh pai thei ka;
 Ei taihsan ngei loh hiel ding thu ei hilh tai,
 A Belam mawlh a ei lungmuon ding.

[V2]
 Thihna luiguom, thihna luiguom,
 Thihna luiguom kana chieh tei ding ka hi;
 Jordan lui kinawk chun ei hihna puo'n a,
 Ziechun lungmuon na a um ka hei.

[V3]
 2. Thihna luiguom chuh kana ka chieh tieng leh;
 Sepgim leh haksatna nicheng bei ta'n a;
 Isu ban thahat tak chun ei pawm intin,
 A kawm achun lungkham ta puo'ng ka.

[V4]
 3. Thihna luiguom chuh kanin chieh mah lengle,
 Zing khawvak lopi hungsuok chuh mu'ng ka ting;
 Jordan galah amau la sak pih ta'ng ka,
 Lungdeih te'n ei ngakna mun achun.

[V5]
 4. Thihna luiguom chuh kana chieh ding ka hi,
 Ka Lalpa chiehna nungsul chuh zui zel ka;
 Luiguom a mei zing kanin ei pui intin,
 Luigal gam hing zing chuh ka tun ma'n.</lyrics>
<title>THROUGH THE VALLEY OF THE SHADOW</title>
<hymn_number>359</hymn_number>
<author>Sam 234</author>
</song>